column5: Not a touch all day,then with 10 minutes of daylight left,this big girl hit.........
WTG Larry. Hey you seem to be putting on a little weight.....but then, so are your fish.  Thanks for the pic.
Hey Larry !..Why don't you head up this way for some Whitefish??  That's a serious looking musky right there
That beast's lip stick makes me want to lean in for a kiss, but those teeth make me hesitate. Nice catch!
You're almost smiling.  That's a slobby buzzer beater fish.
I'd say that was a GREAT day!!!   Awesome fish!!!
Nice fish. That has some meat that's for sure.
great fish...I always seem to pack it in too early
Nice catch.  Look at the teeth on that thing.
Nice fish Larry, the fall windows can be short, and many fall pigs have been taken at dusk, when the rest of the day has been rather uneventful.
Very nice fish but i have to admit Larry...i was hoping to see your post production Photo enhancement abilities at play here
